# 📦 2. Chart.yaml

```yaml
apiVersion: v2
name: mstr-app
description: Master application Helm chart
type: application
version: 0.1.0
appVersion: "1.0"
```

---

# ⚙️ 3. values.yaml (INPUTS FROM ANSIBLE)

```yaml
appid: ""
env: ""
application: ""
version: ""
teamdl: ""

image:
  repository: nginx
  tag: latest
  pullPolicy: IfNotPresent

replicaCount: 1

service:
  type: ClusterIP
  port: 80
```

---

# 🧠 4. _helpers.tpl (MOST IMPORTANT)

This is where enterprise magic happens.

```yaml
{{/*
Generate namespace
*/}}
{{- define "mstr.namespace" -}}
{{- printf "%s-%s-%s" .Values.appid .Values.env .Values.application | lower | regexReplaceAll "[^a-z0-9-]" "-" | trimAll "-" -}}
{{- end }}

{{/*
Common Labels
*/}}
{{- define "mstr.labels" -}}
app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ .Values.application | quote }}
app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Values.appid | quote }}
app.kubernetes.io/version: {{ .Values.version | quote }}
app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Values.teamdl | quote }}
{{- end }}

{{/*
Selector Labels (important for deployment)
*/}}
{{- define "mstr.selectorLabels" -}}
app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ .Values.application | quote }}
app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Values.appid | quote }}
{{- end }}
```

---

# 🚀 5. Deployment.yaml

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: {{ .Values.application }}
  labels:
    {{- include "mstr.labels" . | nindent 4 }}
spec:
  replicas: {{ .Values.replicaCount }}
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      {{- include "mstr.selectorLabels" . | nindent 6 }}
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        {{- include "mstr.labels" . | nindent 8 }}
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: {{ .Values.application }}
          image: "{{ .Values.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.image.tag }}"
          ports:
            - containerPort: 80
```

---

# 🌐 6. Service.yaml

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: {{ .Values.application }}
  labels:
    {{- include "mstr.labels" . | nindent 4 }}
spec:
  type: {{ .Values.service.type }}
  selector:
    {{- include "mstr.selectorLabels" . | nindent 4 }}
  ports:
    - port: {{ .Values.service.port }}
      targetPort: 80
```

