# ▶️ 8. Deploy via Ansible

### Task:

```yaml
- name: Deploy Helm chart
  shell: >
    helm upgrade --install {{ application }}
    ./mstr-app
    --namespace {{ namespace_name }}
    --create-namespace
    --set appid={{ appid }}
    --set env={{ env }}
    --set application={{ application }}
    --set version={{ version }}
    --set teamdl={{ teamdl }}
```

